{"tid":1373443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"催淚煙攻入住宅大廈 有元朗居民吸入氣體感不適","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T15:46:18.000Z","uid":212249,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75fc4a25b802e4cb96cf78956579433212ec809e","tid":1373443,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"警方今日在元朗多處施放催淚彈。元朗居民陳先生目擊，催淚彈除了射向西鐵路軌外，亦射中附近的民居，他們所住的大樓亦受影響。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生指，即使緊閉窗戶也有催淚彈的煙霧攻入，其母親亦吸入氣體，引致氣喘及咳嗽；他批評警方不應在民居發放催淚彈，罔顧市民安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2434237833299063/UzpfSTEwMDAwMzc0NjY3OTI4MTpWSzoyOTc2NzY5ODg1Njk3Mzg5/?sorting_setting=CHRONOLOGICAL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F2434237833299063%2FUzpfSTEwMDAwMzc0NjY3OTI4MTpWSzoyOTc2NzY5ODg1Njk3Mzg5%2F%3Fsorting_setting%3DCHRONOLOGICAL&d=%2FFjBtsZQ5cEfgjMY%2Bqoz3hVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=e2357a25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2434237833299063/UzpfSTEwMDAwMzc0NjY3OTI4MTpWSzoyOTc2NzY5ODg1Njk3Mzg5/?sorting_setting=CHRONOLOGICAL</a>"},{"pid":"fa8452d7b03c52c6668c530902c6704e0199dd9b","tid":1373443,"uid":110332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"係時候成立民間防衛隊做返警察應該做嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n依家咁多證據都證明<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">警察=黑社會</span></span>，依家嘅警察已經失去合法性<br />\n<br />\n首先可以由集體唔交稅開始<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E7XMWCx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE7XMWCx.png&h=73fa9ee1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2dc643d7d2dca4fe7050113ad09b31a812e75ae","tid":1373443,"uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:32:02.000Z","msg":"阿sir濫殺無辜唔洗你教"},{"pid":"c7815597da998e5c4fd67eabb9421a0092de09df","tid":1373443,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"黑警只保護香港(鄉黑) 香港市民有無